650300,128,4974,2,10,1,60,7,Ahu tuyhaṃ pure {saddhā}ti āyasmato sāṭimattiyattherassa gāthā. 
650301,128,4974,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
650302,128,4974,14,35,1,195,21,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ disvā pasannamānaso tālavaṇṭaṃ adāsi. 
650303,128,4974,36,59,1,240,22,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde magadharaṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā {sāṭimattiyo}ti laddhanāmo vayappatto hetusampannatāya āraññakabhikkhūnaṃ santike pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
