650317,128,4980,90,98,1,59,8,Punadivase thero taṃ kāraṇaṃ anāvajjento taṃ gharaṃ agamāsi. 
650318,128,4980,99,103,1,30,4,Tattha manussā anādaraṃ akaṃsu. 
650319,128,4980,104,133,1,201,23,Thero taṃ kāraṇaṃ āvajjento mārassa kiriyaṃ disvā‘‘ tassa gīvāyaṃ kukkurakuṇapaṃ paṭimuñcatū’’ ti adhiṭṭhahitvā tassa mocanatthaṃ upagatena mārena atītadivase katakiriyaṃ kathāpetvā taṃ tajjetvā vissajjesi. 
