650333,128,4991,2,41,1,172,29,"Tattha ahu tuyhaṃ pure saddhā, sā te ajja na {vijjatī}ti, upāsaka, ito pubbe tava mayi‘‘ ayyo dhammacārī samacārī’’ tiādinā saddhā ahosi, sā saddhā te tava ajja idāni na upalabbhati. "
650334,128,4991,42,65,1,146,20,"Tasmā yaṃ tuyhaṃ tuyhamevetan ti catupaccayadānaṃ, tuyhameva etaṃ hotu, na tena mayhaṃ attho, sammā pasannacittena hi dānaṃ nāma dātabbanti adhippāyo. "
650335,128,4991,66,91,1,142,22,"Atha vā yaṃ tuyhaṃ tuyhamevetan ti yaṃ tava mayi ajja agāravaṃ pavattaṃ, taṃ tuyhameva, tassa phalaṃ tayā eva paccanubhavitabbaṃ, na mayāti attho. "
650336,128,4991,92,105,1,109,12,Natthi duccaritaṃ {mamā}ti mama pana duccaritaṃ nāma natthi maggeneva duccaritahetūnaṃ kilesānaṃ samucchinnattā. 
650337,128,4992,2,27,1,170,22,"Aniccā hi calā {saddhā}ti yasmā pothujjanikā saddhā aniccā ekantikā na hoti, tato eva calā assapiṭṭhe ṭhapitakumbhaṇḍaṃ viya, thusarāsimhi nikhātakhāṇukaṃ viya ca anavaṭṭhitā. "
650338,128,4992,28,44,1,84,15,Evaṃ diṭṭhā hi sā {mayā}ti evaṃ bhūtā ca sā saddhā mayā tayi diṭṭhā paccakkhato viditā. 
650339,128,4992,45,65,1,163,18,"Rajjantipi {virajjantī}ti evaṃ tassā anavaṭṭhitattā eva ime sattā kadāci katthaci mittasanthavavasena rajjanti sinehampi karonti, kadāci virajjanti virattacittā honti. "
650340,128,4992,66,85,1,116,17,"Tattha kiṃ jiyyate {munī}ti tasmiṃ puthujjanānaṃ rajjane virajjane ca muni pabbajito kiṃ jiyyati, kā tassa hānīti attho."
650341,128,4993,2,27,1,101,17,"‘ ‘ Sace mama paccaye na gaṇhatha, kathaṃ tumhe yāpethā’’ ti evaṃ mā cintayīti dassento‘‘ paccatī’’ ti gāthamāha. "
650342,128,4993,28,48,1,120,18,"Tassattho munino pabbajitassa bhattaṃ nāma kule kule anugharaṃ divase divase thokaṃ thokaṃ paccate, na ca tuyhaṃ eva gehe. "
650343,128,4993,49,99,1,243,29,"Piṇḍikāya carissāmi, atthi jaṅghabalaṃ {mamā}ti atthi me jaṅghabalaṃ, nāhaṃ obhaggajaṅgho na khañjo na ca pādarogī, tasmā piṇḍikāya missakabhikkhāya carissāmi,‘‘ yathāpi bhamaro pupphan’’ tiādinā( dha. pa.49; netti.123) satthārā vuttanayena piṇḍāya caritvā yāpessāmīti dasseti. "
