650735,128,5338,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
650736,128,5338,14,34,1,195,20,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto vessabhussa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto tādisena kalyāṇamittasannissayena sāsane abhippasanno ahosi. 
650737,128,5338,35,49,1,120,14,So satthari parinibbute tassa dhātuṃ gahetuṃ mahājane ussāhaṃ karonte sayaṃ sabbapaṭhamaṃ gandhodakena citakaṃ nibbāpesi. 
650738,128,5338,50,67,1,153,16,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde veṭhapuranagare rājakule nibbattitvā {abhibhūto}ti laddhanāmo pitu accayena rajjaṃ kāreti. 
650739,128,5338,68,77,1,77,9,Tasmiñca samaye bhagavā janapadacārikaṃ caranto anupubbena taṃ nagaraṃ pāpuṇi. 
650740,128,5338,78,100,1,127,18,Tato so rājā‘‘ bhagavā kira mama nagaraṃ anuppatto’’ ti sutvā satthu santikaṃ gantvā dhammaṃ sutvā dutiyadivase mahādānaṃ pavattesi. 
