650887,129,7,13,32,1,168,17,Ayampi padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto gimhasamaye sūriyātapasantattāya bhūmiyā gacchantaṃ satthāraṃ disvā pasannamānaso chattaṃ adāsi. 
