651843,129,598,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
651844,129,598,12,36,1,199,23,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto ito pañcanavute kappe buddhasuññe loke kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekaṃ paccekabuddhaṃ byādhitaṃ disvā harītakaṃ adāsi . 
651845,129,598,37,52,1,138,14,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kosalaraṭṭhe gahapatikule nibbattitvā {sumano}ti laddhanāmo sukhena vaḍḍhi. 
651846,129,598,53,68,1,123,15,Tassa pana mātulo pabbajitvā arahā hutvā araññe viharanto sumane vayappatte taṃ pabbājetvā caritānukūlaṃ kammaṭṭhānaṃ adāsi. 
651847,129,598,69,79,1,74,10,So tattha yogakammaṃ karonto cattāri jhānāni pañca ca abhiññāyo nibbattesi. 
