652420,129,952,36,57,1,167,18,"Soṇo abhāsi saddhamman ti soḷasa aṭṭhakavaggiyasuttāni soṇo kuṭikaṇṇo, buddhaseṭṭhassa sammāsambuddhassa sammukhā, paccakkhato abhāsīti thero attānameva paraṃ viya avoca. "
652421,129,953,2,25,1,195,20,"Pañcakkhandhe {pariññāyā}ti pañcupādānakkhandhe tīhipi pariññāhi parijānitvā te parijānantoyeva, añjasaṃ ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvayitvā, paramaṃ santiṃ nibbānaṃ pappuyya pāpuṇitvā ṭhito anāsavo. "
