652425,129,956,2,10,1,54,7,Yo eva garūnan tiādikā āyasmato kosiyattherassa gāthā. 
652426,129,956,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
652427,129,956,14,36,1,213,22,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ kusalaṃ upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ disvā pasannacitto ucchukhaṇḍikaṃ adāsi. 
652428,129,956,37,53,1,138,15,"So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde magadharaṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbatti, kosiyo tissa gottavasena nāmaṃ akāsi. "
652429,129,956,54,66,1,95,11,"So viññutaṃ patto āyasmantaṃ dhammasenāpatiṃ abhiṇhaṃ upasaṅkamati, tassa santike dhammaṃ suṇāti. "
652430,129,956,67,77,1,96,10,So tena sāsane paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ anuyuñjanto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
