652493,129,992,2,4,1,32,2,1 . Uruvelakassapattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
652494,129,993,2,11,1,77,6,Chakkanipāte disvāna {pāṭihīrānī}tiādikā āyasmato uruvelakassapattherassa gāthā. 
652495,129,993,12,14,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
652496,129,993,15,50,1,314,33,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ kusalaṃ upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā, vayappatto satthu santike dhammaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ mahāparisānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā, sayampi taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthetvā mahādānaṃ datvā paṇidhānamakāsi. "
652497,129,993,51,68,1,105,12,"Bhagavā cassa anantarāyataṃ disvā,‘‘ anāgate gotamabuddhassa sāsane mahāparisānaṃ aggo bhavissatī’’ ti byākāsi. "
652498,129,994,2,19,1,155,16,So tattha yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā tato cavitvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto ito dvānavutikappamatthake phussassa bhagavato vemātikakaniṭṭhabhātā hutvā nibbatti. 
652499,129,994,20,24,1,36,4,Aññepissa dve kaniṭṭhabhātaro ahesuṃ. 
652500,129,994,25,54,1,248,28,"Te tayopi buddhappamukhaṃ saṅghaṃ paramāya pūjāya pūjetvā yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto amhākaṃ bhagavato nibbattito puretarameva bārāṇasiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule bhātaro hutvā, anukkamena nibbattā gottavasena tayopi kassapā eva nāma jātā. "
652501,129,994,55,60,1,34,5,Te vayappattā tayo vede uggaṇhiṃsu. 
652502,129,994,61,72,1,85,9,"Tesaṃ jeṭṭhabhātikassa pañca māṇavakasatāni parivāro, majjhimassa tīṇi, kaniṭṭhassa dve. "
652503,129,994,73,83,1,81,10,Te attano ganthe sāraṃ olokentā diṭṭhadhammikameva atthaṃ disvā pabbajjaṃ rocesuṃ. 
652504,129,994,84,107,1,199,22,"Tesu jeṭṭhabhātā attano parivārena saddhiṃ uruvelaṃ gantvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā uruvelakassapo nāma jāto mahāgaṅgānadīvaṅke pabbajito nadīkassapo nāma jāto, gayāsīse pabbajito gayākassapo nāma jāto. "
652505,129,995,2,64,1,541,50,"Evaṃ tesu isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā tattha tattha vasantesu bahūnaṃ divasānaṃ accayena amhākaṃ bodhisatto mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamitvā, paṭividdhasabbaññutaññāṇo anukkamena dhammacakkaṃ pavattetvā, pañcavaggiyatthere arahatte patiṭṭhāpetvā yasappamukhe pañcapaññāsa sahāyake vinetvā saṭṭhi arahante‘‘ caratha, bhikkhave, cārikan’’ ti vissajjetvā, bhaddavaggiye vinetvā uruvelakassapassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā vasanatthāya agyāgāraṃ pavisitvā , tattha katanāgadamanaṃ ādiṃ katvā aḍḍhuḍḍhasahassehi pāṭihāriyehi uruvelakassapaṃ saparisaṃ vinetvā pabbājesi. "
652506,129,995,65,76,1,90,11,Tassa pabbajitabhāvaṃ ñatvā itarepi dve bhātaro saparisā āgantvā satthu santike pabbajiṃsu. 
652507,129,995,77,81,1,51,4,Sabbeva ehibhikkhū iddhimayapattacīvaradharā ahesuṃ. 
652508,129,996,2,14,1,120,12,Satthā taṃ samaṇasahassaṃ ādāya gayāsīsaṃ gantvā piṭṭhipāsāṇe nisinno ādittapariyāyadesanāya sabbe arahatte patiṭṭhāpesi. 
