652829,129,1205,44,64,1,141,19,"Yathā etaṃ etarahi matasarīraṃ tesaṃ dhammānaṃ apagamā na kiñci kiriyaṃ dasseti, tathā idaṃ mama sarīrampi tesaṃ dhammānaṃ apagamā nassatevāti. "
652830,129,1205,65,88,1,138,20,"Yathā ca idaṃ mama sarīraṃ etarahi susāne na mataṃ na sayitaṃ, na uddhumātakādibhāvaṃ upagataṃ, tathā etaṃ etarahi matasarīrampi pubbe ahosi. "
652831,129,1205,89,103,1,114,13,"Yathā panetaṃ etarahi matasarīraṃ susāne sayitaṃ uddhumātakādibhāvaṃ upagataṃ, tathā idaṃ mama sarīrampi bhavissati. "
652832,129,1205,104,121,1,117,16,"Atha vā yathā idaṃ mama sarīraṃ asuci duggandhaṃ jegucchaṃ paṭikkūlaṃ aniccaṃ dukkhaṃ anattā, tathā etaṃ matasarīrampi. "
652833,129,1205,122,133,1,91,10,"Yathā vā etaṃ matasarīraṃ asuciādisabhāvañceva aniccādisabhāvañca, tathā idaṃ mama sarīrampi. "
652834,129,1205,134,160,1,167,25,"Yathā adho tathā uddhan ti yathā nābhito adho heṭṭhā ayaṃ kāyo asuci duggandho jeguccho paṭikkūlo anicco dukkho anattā ca, tathā uddhaṃ nābhito upari asuciādisabhāvo ca. "
652835,129,1205,161,177,1,93,13,"Yathā uddhaṃ tathā {adho}ti yathā ca nābhito, uddhaṃ asuciādisabhāvo, tathā adho nābhito heṭṭhāpi. "
652836,129,1206,2,31,1,110,16,"Yathā divā tathā rattin ti yathā ayaṃ kāyo divā‘‘ akkhimhā akkhigūthako’’ tiādinā( su. ni.199) asuci paggharati, tathā rattimpi. "
652837,129,1206,32,52,1,126,17,"Yathā rattiṃ tathā {divā}ti yathā ca rattiṃ ayaṃ kāyo asuci paggharati, tathā divāpi, nayimassa kālavibhāgena aññathābhāvoti attho. "
652838,129,1206,53,73,1,124,18,"Yathā pure tathā {pacchā}ti yathā ayaṃ kāyo pure pubbe taruṇakāle asuci duggandho jeguccho paṭikkūlo, tathā ca pacchā jiṇṇakāle. "
