653071,129,1322,29,54,1,153,17,Idāni yathāvuttaguṇavisesayuttaṃ dhammaṃ sarūpato dassento‘‘ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko’’ ti vatvā punapi tassa katipaye guṇe vibhāvetuṃ‘‘ dukkhūpasamano sivo’’ tiādimāha. 
