653197,129,1389,49,62,1,116,12,"Attahitaparahitānaṃ sādhanato sādhunā katakiccena anuruddhena sādhu ubhayahitasādhako, suṭṭhu vā ājañño kārito damito. "
653198,129,1389,63,69,1,67,6,Aggavijjāya vinīto asekkhabhāvāpādanena sikkhito sikkhāpitoti attho. 
653199,129,1390,2,43,1,274,32,So sāmaṇero sumano paramaṃ santiṃ nibbānaṃ patvā aggamaggādhigamena adhigantvā sacchikatvā attapaccakkhaṃ katvā akuppataṃ arahattaphalaṃ appicchabhāvassa paramukkaṃsagatattā mā maṃ {jaññā}ti maṃ‘‘ ayaṃ khīṇāsavo’’ ti vā‘‘ chaḷabhiñño’’ ti vā kocipi mā jāneyyāti icchati abhikaṅkhatīti. 
