654138,129,1928,22,34,1,120,12,Cūḷapanthako pana kassapassa bhagavato sāsane pabbajitvā vīsati vassasahassāni odātakasiṇakammaṃ katvā devapure nibbatti. 
654139,129,1928,35,57,1,149,18,Apadāne pana‘‘ cūḷapanthako padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle tāpaso hutvā himavante vasanto tattha bhagavantaṃ disvā pupphacchattena pūjaṃ akāsī’’ ti āgataṃ. 
