659631,129,5115,21,56,1,180,23,Taṃ sutvā‘‘ bhaddaṃ tayā suṭṭhu vuttan’’ ti sirasā viya sampaṭicchanto tāvadeva thokaṃ apakkamitvā parimaṇḍalaṃ nivāsetvā‘‘ mādisānaṃ ayampi dosoyevā’’ ti dassento‘‘ anaṅgaṇassā’’ ti gāthamāha. 
