659979,129,5313,2,17,1,65,10,"Yena pana saṃsaggo kātabbo, taṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ saddhena cā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
659980,129,5313,18,27,1,83,7,"Tattha {saddhenā}ti kammakammaphalasaddhāya ceva, ratanattayasaddhāya ca samannāgatena. "
659981,129,5313,28,32,1,36,3,{Pesalenā}ti piyasīlena sīlasampannena. 
659982,129,5313,33,40,1,73,6,{Paññavatā}ti udayatthagāminiyā nibbedhikāya paññāya vasena paññāsampannena. 
659983,129,5313,41,46,1,67,4,{Bahussutenā}ti pariyattipaṭivedhabāhusaccānaṃ pāripūriyā bahussutena. 
659984,129,5313,47,60,1,111,12,{Bhaddo}ti tena tādisena sādhunā saṅgamo bhaddo sundaro kalyāṇo diṭṭhadhammikādibhedaṃ atthaṃ āvahatīti adhippāyo. 
659985,129,5314,2,18,1,144,15,Passa cittakatan tiādikā satta gāthā attano rūpasampattiṃ disvā kāmasaññaṃ uppādentiyā uttarāya nāma upāsikāya kāyavicchandajananatthaṃ bhāsitā .
659986,129,5314,19,30,1,70,7,‘‘ Ambapāliṃ gaṇikaṃ disvā vikkhittacittānaṃ ovādadānatthan’’ tipi vadanti. 
659987,129,5314,31,35,1,23,4,Tā heṭṭhā vuttatthā eva. 
659988,129,5315,2,13,1,81,9,Bahussuto {cittakathī}tiādikā dve gāthā therena arahattaṃ patvā udānavasena bhāsitā. 
659989,129,5315,14,18,1,29,3,Tattha {paricārako}ti upaṭṭhāko. 
659990,129,5315,19,25,1,60,5,Seyyaṃ {kappetī}ti arahattappattisamanantaraṃ sayitattā vuttaṃ. 
659991,129,5315,26,53,1,194,25,"Thero hi bahudeva rattiṃ caṅkamena vītināmetvā sarīraṃ utuṃ gāhāpetuṃ ovarakaṃ pavisitvā sayituṃ mañcake nisinno pādā ca bhūmito muttā, appattañca sīsaṃ bimbohanaṃ, etthantare arahattaṃ patvā sayi. "
659992,129,5316,2,22,1,173,16,"{Khīṇāsavo}ti parikkhīṇacaturāsavo, tato eva catūhipi yogehi visaṃyutto, rāgasaṅgādīnaṃ atikkantattā saṅgātīto, sabbaso kilesapariḷāhassa vūpasantattā sunibbuto sītibhūtoti attho. "
659993,129,5317,2,11,1,77,8,Yasmiṃ patiṭṭhitā {dhammā}ti theraṃ uddissa khīṇāsavamahābrahmunā bhāsitā gāthā. 
659994,129,5317,12,29,1,102,13,Upaṭṭhitāya hi dhammasaṅgītiyā theraṃ uddissa yehi bhikkhūhi‘‘ eko bhikkhu vissagandhaṃ vāyatī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
659995,129,5317,30,42,1,135,11,"Atha thero adhigate arahatte sattapaṇṇiguhādvāraṃ saṅghassa sāmaggīdānatthaṃ āgato, tassa khīṇāsavabhāvappakāsanena suddhāvāsamahābrahmā. "
659996,129,5317,43,55,1,59,8,Te bhikkhū lajjāpento‘‘ yasmiṃ patiṭṭhitā dhammā’’ ti gāthamāha. 
659997,129,5317,56,66,1,89,9,Tassattho– buddhassa bhagavato dhammā teneva adhigatā paveditā ca paṭivedhapariyattidhammā. 
659998,129,5317,67,85,1,172,15,"Yasmiṃ purisavisese patiṭṭhitā, soyaṃ gottato gotamo dhammabhaṇḍāgāriko saupādisesanibbānassa adhigatattā idāni anupādisesanibbānagamane magge patiṭṭhahi, tassa ekaṃsabhāgīti. "
659999,129,5318,2,8,1,58,6,Athekadivasaṃ gopakamoggallāno nāma brāhmaṇo theraṃ pucchi–
660000,129,5318,9,28,1,91,13,"‘‘ tvaṃ bahussutoti buddhassa sāsane pākaṭo, kittakā dhammā te satthārā bhāsitā, tayā dhāritā’’ ti? "
